nodes.text: Mosh was a shuttle pilot who served aboard Outbound Flight. After a movement against Jedi Master Jorus C'baoth had arisen on board and the passengers hoped to be able to get Thrawn to free them from C'baoth, Mosh brought a group of the dissatisfied to D-Eins with a shuttle, and Dillian Pressor was the initiator. In the hangar at D-Eins, however, they were unable to leave the ferry because C'baoth locked the hatch with the Force.
